+| **Gate** | Check produced artifacts against ground truth (returns Verdict) | async | L3 Harness |
+| **Router** | Choose a candidate or next action (+ `feedback()`) | sync | L1 Framework |
+| **Composer** | Combine retrieved material under budget constraints (takes `&dyn Scorer`) | sync | L2 Scaffold |
+| **Policy** | React to recent activity and emit follow-on Engrams | sync | L3-L4 |
 
